snippet.title: Savage online trolls flock to social media to viciously attack Amber Sherlock...
snippet.description:
Amber Sherlock has become the victim of savage online trolling after a video of her scolding her Channel 9 co-worker Julie Snook for wearing the wrong coloured dress went viral.
Although the 45-year-old hasn't updated her Instagram page in over two weeks, her most recent posts have been filled with vicious comments from viewers who were unimpressed with her 'diva' behaviour.
